keyFacts: The document is a travel voucher notification from the DOJ's E2 Solutions system dated February 21, 2020.
The travel was specifically for 'Epstein Investigation - Witness interview' under purpose code R20NYS13403.
The travel occurred from February 19 to February 20, 2020, with total expenses of $628.07 and an estimated trip cost of $973.89.
The voucher status was 'Pending Voucher Approval' at the time of the notification.
The document indicates ongoing investigative activity related to the Epstein case in early 2020.
